list of protected column names

Data fields defined in the protectedColumns list are protected from being set in massive assignments, such as setData(Map). Instead these fields have to be set directly by using setData(String) or setData(String, Object).

java.util.List<E> extraFields

Extra fields are fields that are needed by the model during a transaction process but not recorded in the database table.

For example, password_confirmation.
